KitKat::

She was in the CR chamber. She was being repaired, but it was slow 
going.  She was in such bad shape, it was going to be a while before 
she got out of there. However, the repairs had gone far enough to 
show her predacon emblem on her shoulder.  She felt her whole body 
tingle as the repairs continued.
